Well he had - I mean, it's obvious they're going to give a man a bit more. I always give ours a bit more that I get for myself. Well I always think to myself well - they want it more. Yes, yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15211515 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5471496\charrsid2041182 Were you allowed to talk during meals or not?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid283337 MG  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5471496\charrsid2041182 We didn't -
