\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15211515 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5471496\charrsid2041182 Could you ask for a second helping?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid283337 MG  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5471496\charrsid2041182 Sometimes if it was there you could.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15211515 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5471496\charrsid2041182 Were you expected to hold your knife and fork in a certain way and sit in a certain way?
