\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15211515 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5471496\charrsid2041182 You learnt it the hard way?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid283337 MG  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5471496\charrsid2041182 Oh yes. There was none of that business now as there are - is today on no.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15211515 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5471496\charrsid2041182 Could you bring toys or books to the table?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid283337 MG  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5471496\charrsid2041182 Oh - I don't think I ever seen a - a toy or a book.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15211515 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5471496\charrsid2041182 You never had one?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid283337 MG  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5471496\charrsid2041182 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15211515 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5471496\charrsid2041182 When could you leave the table - when you'd finished or did you have to wait until everybody else had finished?
