on those days, I can't understand the people those days. Mind you I think it is the way - the way they've been brought up.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15211515 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5471496\charrsid2041182 You can't blame them, it's the attitude as they were brought up?
