\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid283337 MG  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5471496\charrsid2041182 It wasn't - no, I told him the next man I marry - I was going to marry him for his money not for his looks. He told me once you know I'd }{
