Well I used to go canvassing for - oh yes, I've canvassed up 'til last - was it last year - the year Dick Crawshore got in. 'Cos my son - the son I've lost - and Dick Crawshore were like that - oh yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15211515 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5471496\charrsid2041182 So this involved you of course?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid283337 MG  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5471496\charrsid2041182 Yes, well I mean I have been for many, many years.
