\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15211515 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5471496\charrsid2041182 Did either of you go to any clubs, institutes or pubs - where would he have gone to play whist?
